Master Schedule Details
The Scheduling Module is designed with flexibility as a primary feature to accommodate each individual schools unique scheduling processes and business rules. The Master Schedule component provides schools an easy to use solution that will automatically generate student schedules. Run preliminary Master Schedules to determine which schedule meets the individual school and student requirements. In addition, the Scheduling Module is feature rich including the ability to block schedule, link courses and sections, provide unlimited number of sections per course.

Master Schedule Module features and benefits:

    Customized Bell to Bell Schedule – including days, periods, rotational or block
    Student Course Requests – set defaults by grade level, easy input of student requests
    Flexible Teacher Management Schedule – accommodates part time, full time teachers
    Master Schedule Builder – determine sections and automatically generates master schedule
    Printing – print reports, teacher schedules, student schedules, room availability and rosters
